Name:           Greater Demon
Short Name:     greater
Level Required: 27

Description:
  In addition to its fang, claw, and tail attacks, the Greater Demon
  uses a multi-tentacle attack to slash at many foes at once.

Commands:
  - summon greater: Summons it to you         (costs 250 sp)
  - catt <monster>: Makes it attack <monster> (costs 10 sp)
  - cstop:          Makes it stop fighting    (costs 20 sp)
  - ban greater:    Banishes it               (costs 40 sp)
